#

Spicy Guacamole

10 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeLow-Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerSnackEasy

Description

A creamy and zesty avocado dip with a fiery twist from jalapeños, perfect for snacking or as a party appetizer.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • diced jalapeños: 1 tablespoon
  • red onion, finely chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • fresh cilantro, chopped: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
